cd u-boot
tools/buildman/buildman -H                           # 帮助信息，buildman 设置文件 /HOME/.buildman
tools/buildman/buildman --fetch-arch all
tools/buildman/buildman --fetch-arch arm             # 获取 arm 架构
tools/buildman/buildman -k rpi_2                     # 编译树莓派2



the Embedded Linux Development Kit (ELDK) version 5.8. This release is based on Yocto v1.8.1 ("fido")
